{"tid":2370030,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打搵到十幾年前一篇有關屯門既潮文","createTime":"2021-01-17T16:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T16:22:35.000Z","uid":72411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"108812bd5a17acd7d3428a25d1d67052b837dc85","tid":2370030,"uid":72411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"話說十幾年前仲係小學生<br />\n仲會上香討果啲靈異區睇文<br />\n果陣記得睇過有篇on9文話點解屯門多色魔<br />\n因為填完海個地型好似女人個閪 所以陰氣重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知篇文真係好鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係有次同fd傾開計 我講左睇過篇咁既野之後<br />\n比佢地笑鳩我係自己作出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果有人可以搵得番呢篇野出黎就好喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}